data.description:
This recently renovated 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home is located less than 2 miles from the sports and entertainment district in Downtown Phoenix. Watch the Suns or D-Backs, your favorite team when they come into town. Or enjoy your downtime at CityScape Urban Shopping and Entertainment Complex. 

Other Fees:
Security Deposit: $800.00 (on approved credit) 
Water/Sewer/Trash: $75.00 
Pet Rent: $35.00 per pet (max. 2 pet) 
Pet Fee: $300.00 ($350 for 2 pets) 
Application Fee: $45.00 
Rental Tax: 2.3% 
Resident Benefits Package: 2.0%
Non-Refundable Administration Fee: $150.00 

Electricity: APS

Renters Insurance is required
